yum install cifs-utils    => installing cifs on linux
mkdir Desktop/share   => making a folder in linux for mount
mount.cifs //192.168.1.248/linux /home/hari/Desktop/linux -o user=gautamhp    => Provide PW from the windows machine

On Third line
"IP addrress" is your Windows IP Address
"_DevOps" is the folder from windows machine to share
"/home/hari/Desktop/share" is the location on the linux machine
"GAUTAMHP" is the Windows UserName
